DUSSELDORF, Respondent, v. WARREN, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

Additional General Term.

December 16, 1895.) Action by John E. Dusseldorf against Charles J. Warren. R. R. Perry, for appellant. Coleman J. Donohue, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
